            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.27 - Correct suspend_data Interpretation</h3>

            <h4>Important Fix</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>"l" field is FURTHEST progress, NOT current position</li>
                <li>Removed "l" from current position detection</li>
                <li>Poll mechanism is now source of truth for current position</li>
                <li>suspend_data only updates furthestSlide, not current slide</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Removed "l" field priority from extractSlideFromParsedData()</li>
                <li>Removed "l" field regex from extractSlideFromText()</li>
                <li>suspend_data tracking now only updates furthestSlide variable</li>
                <li>sendProgressUpdate() no longer overrides current position from suspend_data</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.26: Skip score-based position during intercept</li>
                <li>v2.0.25: Prioritize "l" field (incorrect - now fixed)</li>
                <li>v2.0.24: Unlimited intercepts within 10s window</li>
                <li>v2.0.22: Re-enable write interception (l field only)</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
